scription\\\":\\\"The structured question to ask the user\\\"}},\\\"required\\\":[\\\"question\\\"],\\\"additionalProperties\\\":false,\\\"$schema\\\":\\\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\\\"}\\n```\\n</structured-output>\"}]}"
